        "subject": "LU-17077 tests: User correct group id in RUNAS",
        "message": "LU-17077 tests: User correct group id in RUNAS\n\nsanity-quota/63 RUNAS was using the same id for\ngid. This patch adds new RUNAS3 global variable\nwhich uses the correct gid.\n\nFor quota_usr:\n$ getent passwd quota_usr\nquota_usr:x:1001:1002::/home/quota_usr:/bin/bash\n\nDebug run logs original code:\nrunas -u 1001 -g 1001 ...\n\nDebug run logs changed code:\nrunas -u 1001 -g 1002 ...\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanity-quota\nSigned-off-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@aeoncomputing.com>\nChange-Id: Ib426f539a2301cd40db06b4d4f002d7b21577dce\n"
      },
